title: You Want to See My Pecks and Booty Too

description:
Wednesday 10/10 - Today on the show we had actor Taye Diggs in the building, where he spoke about feeling insecure in the beginning of his career, classic film roles and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to yet another Florida man for imposing ban on customers warming urine in the microwave and Angela helped some listeners during "Ask Yee".
